  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0da2\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dca, \u0db6\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dca\u0db0\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0dbd\u0ddc\u0d9a\u0dd4 \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db4\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sajith assigns a big task to Buddhi",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Matara District Parliamentarian Buddhika Pathirana has been appointed as the General Secretary of the Secretariat, which has been set up by the Leader of the Opposition's National Program to implement the social reforms demanded by the people.",
        "The appointment was made by Leader of the Opposition Sajith Primadasa.",
        "MP Buddhika Pathirana said that this Secretariat was established to create a modern Sri Lanka with the aim of finding solutions to the severe economic, political and social crisis facing Sri Lanka today.",
        "The purpose of this Secretariat is to reach an agreement for the social transformation demanded by the people and to establish a national program for social reform, said Mr. Buddhika Pathirana."
      ],
